desc.en:
This overhead city is under the jurisdiction of Green Sea Company.

It is a Minecraft city. You can join the server and it will be opened in the future.

Although it is under the jurisdiction of Green Sea, there are still many companies.

• Under the Green Sea

Green Sea Crystal Iron, under the jurisdiction of @swcdjzc (GitHub name)

Green Sea High-Speed Railway Light Rail, under the jurisdiction of @WZDXPGD (GitHub name)

Green Sea Head Office, under the jurisdiction of @WZDXPGD
